Competition: Rio de Janeiro Championship 
Season: 1998


First Stage 
[qualifying competition for second stage]

Round: 1 [Jan 25]
Madureira     0-0 Friburguense   [Jan 24]
America       awd Itaperuna      [originally 1-1; awarded 1-0 to America?] 
Olaria        0-0 Volta Redonda  

Round: 2 [Jan 28]
Volta Redonda 0-1 America
Friburguense  0-0 Olaria 
Itaperuna     awd Madureira      [originally 1-0; awarded 1-0 to Madureira as
                                  Itaperuna had 4 ineligible players]  
Round: 3 [Feb 1]
Madureira     3-1 America        [Jan 31]
Olaria        3-1 Itaperuna      [10 paying fans...]
Friburguense  2-1 Volta Redonda

Round: 4 [Feb 4]
Madureira     0-1 Volta Redonda
Itaperuna     1-3 Friburguense
America       0-2 Olaria

Round: 5 [Feb 8]
Olaria        0-0 Madureira   
Volta Redonda 0-1 Itaperuna
America       0-1 Friburguense

Round: 6 [Feb 12]
Friburguense  4-2 Madureira
Volta Redonda 2-1 Olaria
Itaperuna     1-1 America

Round: 7 [Feb 14]
Madureira     4-0 Itaperuna
America       2-0 Volta Redonda  [Feb 15]
Olaria        3-3 Friburguense

Round: 8 [Feb 18]
America       1-1 Madureira
Volta Redonda 1-0 Friburguense
Itaperuna     0-2 Olaria

Round: 9 [Feb 26]
Friburguense  3-0 Itaperuna
Olaria        3-0 America
Volta Redonda 0-2 Madureira

Round: 10 [Mar 1]
Madureira     3-1 Olaria
Itaperuna     3-4 Volta Redonda
Friburguense  2-1 America

