[Relegation of Itaperuna later revoked; promoted: Cabofriense.]

Second Stage

Automatic qualifiers: Americano, Bangu, Botafogo, Flamengo, Fluminense,
                      Vasco da Gama
 
First Phase (Taça Guanabara)

Round: 1 [Mar 10]
Madureira     3-2 Botafogo      [Mar 7]
Americano     1-1 Friburguense
Vasco         4-3 Fluminense    [Mar 8]
Bangu         2-1 Flamengo

Round: 2 [Mar 14]
Bangu         1-3 Madureira  
Flamengo      3-0 Botafogo
Fluminense    1-1 Americano
Friburguense  0-3 Vasco         [Apr 7] 

Round: 3 [Mar 18]
Vasco         5-0 Americano     [Feb 1]
Friburguense  1-2 Fluminense
Botafogo      0-0 Bangu
Flamengo      2-0 Madureira

Round: 4 [Mar 22]
Botafogo      0-2 Friburguense  [Mar 24]
Americano     2-1 Bangu
Fluminense    0-0 Flamengo
Madureira     0-4 Vasco         [Apr 12]

Round: 5 [Mar 29]
Fluminense    2-0 Madureira
Americano     1-2 Flamengo
