Friburguense  1-1 Bangu

Round: 6 [Apr 1]
Vasco         1-0 Bangu         [Jan 18]
Flamengo      3-0 Friburguense
Madureira     2-2 Americano     [Apr 2]
Botafogo      1-1 Fluminense

Round: 7 [Apr 8]
Americano     1-2 Botafogo
Bangu         2-1 Fluminense    [Apr 5]
Madureira     2-1 Friburguense
Flamengo      0-0 Vasco         [Apr 19]

