Second Phase (Taça Rio de Janeiro)

Round: 1 [Apr 22]
Fluminense    1-0 Friburguense  [Apr 22]
Flamengo      0-0 Bangu
Americano     0-1 Vasco   
Botafogo      1-1 Madureira

Round: 2 [Apr 26]
Vasco         3-1 Friburguense
Botafogo      3-3 Flamengo
Americano     1-1 Fluminense  
Madureira     2-2 Bangu

Round: 3 [May 10]
Bangu         2-0 Friburguense  [Apr 30]
Madureira     1-0 Fluminense    [May 1]
Flamengo      4-2 Americano     
Vasco         w/o Botafogo      [Botafogo dns, awarded 2-0 to Vasco]

Round: 4 [May 3]
Madureira     2-3 Flamengo
Bangu         2-1 Botafogo
Friburguense  3-1 Americano     
Vasco         0-2 Fluminense    [May 21]

Round: 5 [May 6]
Friburguense  0-1 Flamengo
Fluminense    1-1 Botafogo
Americano     1-0 Madureira     [May 7]
Bangu         0-1 Vasco         [May 14]

Round: 6 [May 13]
Vasco         2-0 Madureira     [Apr 29]
Bangu         0-0 Americano     [May 12]
Friburguense  4-2 Botafogo
Flamengo      awd Fluminense    [neither side showed up, awarded 0-2 against both]

Round: 7 [May 17]
Madureira     1-2 Friburguense  [May 10]
Botafogo      2-0 Americano     [May 16]
Vasco         awd Flamengo      [Flamengo dns, awarded 2-0 to Vasco]
Fluminense    5-1 Bangu


