* 8.Americano       7  1  2  4   5-11   5
*
*Vasco da Gama wins second phase, and thereby, as winners of first phase,
*the Rio de Janeiro state championship 1998.

Topscorers:
Romário (Flamengo), 10 gols.
Roni (Fluminense), 9.
Messias (Madureira), 7.


